{"tid":2515403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"G7布林肯與英外相記者會，記者問：G7目的是聯合民主國家共同對抗中國和俄羅斯的獨裁專制嗎？","createTime":"2021-05-04T03:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T05:26:23.000Z","uid":294518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d3583b9612894f9d5c95a4c798769062b9b1a7a8","tid":2515403,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"G7布林肯與英外相記者會<br />\n<br />\n記者問：G7目的是聯合民主國家共同對抗中國和俄羅斯的獨裁專制嗎？<br />\n布林肯說，對於俄羅斯，非常歡迎俄走正確的道路，美國願意與俄合作。而對於中國，美國的目的不是壓制中國，而且是要對抗任何挑戰「基於規則的國際秩序」的人，這是為了世界人民的利益，也是為了中國人民的利益<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZanXixi/status/1389346015417884672?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZanXixi%2Fstatus%2F1389346015417884672%3Fs%3D20&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=1958913c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZanXixi%2Fstatus%2F1389346015417884672%3Fs%3D20&h=ddb167c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZanXixi/status/1389346015417884672?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"1f7e535f3162627967227b2bc725429e0e16d2cc","tid":2515403,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}